Country: US

Released: 03 Apr 1968

Genre: Rock

Style: Psychedelic Rock

Notes:

Released in a gatefold cover. "Wow" album was originally released and sold together with "Grape Jam" album. At the end of A4, an announcer kindly reminds the listener to get up and change their turntable to 78 rpm, as the next song has been pressed at 78 rpm. There is a silent locked groove before track A5. Versions of this pressing exist with and without the band name on the record's label. Lyrics © Copyright 1968 South Star Music.
